%h1 All Classes
= link_to '[+] Add Class', new_admin_klass_path
%p This is a listing of all schools in the system. You must create a school before you can add students to it.

%table.striped{:width => '100%'}
  %tr
    %th Name
    %th Default Password
  - @klasses.each do |klass|
    %tr.clickable{:'data-href' => admin_klass_path(klass)}
      %td= klass.name
      %td= klass.default_password